STATE of North Carolina
v.
Charles Antonio MEANS No. 266P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 23, 2018 Mr. Charles Antonio Means, for Means, Charles Antonio Mr. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C. Ms. Susan I. Doyle, District Attorney, for State

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 22nd of August 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Johnston County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 23rd of August 2018."
